#include <iostream>
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int LeapYear(int y)
{
    if(y % 100 == 0)
    {
        return (y % 400 == 0);
    }
    else
    {
        return (y % 4 == 0);
    }
}

int main() 
{
    int N;
    int day,year,mon,tot;
    int casenum = 0;
    int totdays[] = {31,59,90,120,151,181,212,243,273,304,334,365};
    int totdaysleap[] = {31,60,91,121,152,182,213,244,274,305,335,366};
    map<string,int> month;
    month["JAN"] = 0;
    month["FEB"] = 1;
    month["MAR"] = 2;
    month["APR"] = 3;
    month["MAY"] = 4;
    month["JUN"] = 5;
    month["JUL"] = 6;
    month["AUG"] = 7;
    month["SEP"] = 8;
    month["OCT"] = 9;
    month["NOV"] = 10;
    month["DEC"] = 11;
    
    string inp;
    
    scanf("%d", &N);
    
    while(N--)
    {
        tot = 0;
        casenum++;
        cin >> inp;
        
        day = std::stoi(inp.substr(0,2));
        year = std::stoi(inp.substr(7));
        mon = month[inp.substr(3,3)];
        
        if(mon != 0)
        {
            if(LeapYear(year))
            {
                tot = totdaysleap[mon - 1];
            }
            else
            {
                tot = totdays[mon - 1];
            }
        }
        
        tot += day;
        
        cout << "Case " << casenum << ": ";
        
        if(tot <= 300)
        {
            cout << tot << " Hundreds" << endl;
        }
        else if(tot <= 360)
        {
            tot -= 300;
            cout << tot << " Tens" << endl;
        }
        else
        {
            tot -= 360;
            cout << tot << " Ones" << endl;
        }
    }
	return 0;
}
